{"tid":1153988,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"無視荷里活反對　康城照向阿倫狄龍致敬","createTime":"2019-05-14T03:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T17:28:48.000Z","uid":41343,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"32fe8fab5e74da8a00a0662bc580165a5bdee6ac","tid":1153988,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T03:55:08.000Z","msg":"《第72屆康城電影節》即將舉行，早前大會宣布今年「特別金棕櫚獎」（Honorary Palme d'Or）將會頒發給，法國著名男星阿倫狄龍（Alain Delon）向他致敬，不過唔係人人都贊同，好似喺荷里活嗰邊就有唔少人反對，佢哋仲發起簽名運動指曾涉家暴及反同嘅阿倫狄龍唔應該得到表揚。 <br />\n<br />\n在電影節開幕前，藝術總監Thierry Fremaux明確表示，頒獎給阿倫狄龍將不會受到影響：「我們不是頒發諾貝爾和平獎，而是對電影職業生涯的致敬，我們獎勵的是演員阿倫狄龍，他有表達自己的自由。今天要向某人致敬是很難，因為總會有人對他的一生進行放大鏡式的審查，康城並不需要對政治完美承擔責任。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190514/mobile/bkn-20190514081020573-0514_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190514%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190514081020573-0514_00862_001.html&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT1LdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=7533b84f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190514/mobile/bkn-20190514081020573-0514_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4df264b92ad7f1d3f1df1464a36bcd8ad77bfc29","tid":1153988,"uid":79355,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:48:45.000Z","msg":"講得啱丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n荷里活班左膠乜都管"},{"pid":"f106130ad01986934f9809e0fb41e5bb3f04a305","tid":1153988,"uid":49247,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:40:07.000Z","msg":"法國佬左膠得黎都仲有返d理智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1463cdf35faf9ce8964902326c366ce497805e","tid":1153988,"uid":103325,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:04:39.000Z","msg":"睇錯咗阿倫同埋狄龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73faad9d61e88b4bb727e6c690a84ddd7676846","tid":1153988,"uid":167426,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>《第72屆康城電影節》即將舉行，早前大會宣布今年「特別金棕櫚獎」（Honorary Palme d'Or）將會頒發給，法國著名男星阿倫狄龍（Alain Delon）向他致敬，不過唔係人人都贊同，好似喺荷里活嗰邊就有唔少人反對，佢哋仲發起簽名運動指曾涉家暴及反同嘅阿倫狄龍唔應該得到表揚。 <br />\n<br />\n在電影節開幕前，藝術總監Thierry Fremaux明確表示，頒獎給阿倫狄龍將不會受到影響：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我們不是頒發諾貝爾和平獎，而是對電影職業生涯的致敬</span>，我們獎勵的是演員阿倫狄龍，他有表達自己的自由。今天要向某人致敬是很難，因為總會有人對他的一生進行放大鏡式的審查，康城並不需要對政治完美承擔責任。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190514/mobile/bkn-20190514081020573-0514_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190514%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190514081020573-0514_00862_001.html&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT1LdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=7533b84f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190514/mobile/bkn-20190514081020573-0514_00862_001.html</a></blockquote><br />\n啱啊<br />\n傻9左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab7da50dabdcb58f6e0e5602355f680f397d462","tid":1153988,"uid":232575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T17:28:48.000Z","msg":"咁成龍呢?"}]}